{"tid":2488055,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"六旬漢涉6．12一年帶頭叫「死黑警」被控擾亂秩序 今判處40天即時監禁","createTime":"2021-04-14T03:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T14:18:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9f9846f08f906659642e8b9fc5eb86b06d4bf329","tid":2488055,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15012&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvov2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=98cf5add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15012</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#徐綺薇主任裁判官 #判刑<br />\n👤陶 (60) #20200612旺角  <br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為<br />\n被控於2020年6月12日在旺角奶路臣街與彌敦道交界、旺角站E1出口外的公眾地方，作出喧嘩或擾亂秩序的行為，意圖激使他人破壞社會安寧，或其上述行為相當可能會導致社會安寧破壞。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------<br />\n🙇🏻&zwj;♂️被告認罪🙇🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n<br />\n速報：被告罪名成立，考慮整體案情及辯方求情後，徐官決定以60日即時監禁作量刑起點，由於被告認罪，刑期扣減1/3至40日，詳情後補。<br />\n<br />\n‼️40天即時監禁‼️<br />\n<br />\n💛感謝臨時直播員💛"},{"pid":"7f8ea373a1b67ce24081c7050a214c13a7b78601","tid":2488055,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee52d606c3ffe30a3ebdfba7c2f5ec3a6e0c531","tid":2488055,"uid":110043,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:43:48.000Z","msg":"咁都40日<br />\non99"},{"pid":"0754b41af787838e2ed960175ba18ad6fe402912","tid":2488055,"uid":210807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"wtf&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b002408fbbf9cb1a5a9935f977bcb4e20b60eb03","tid":2488055,"uid":32669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,