i\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b643cee3d7d340d269c3881b50450fdf434de3dc","tid":2488055,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac73f10acacdbb4d0db1b0c579d80cf1fc5b18f1","tid":2488055,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c591081e5842965637733356eb65e0367831b9c","tid":2488055,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/14c880e956fe12725413ff47722f7518/stheadline/news_res/2020/06/10/490296/i_src_036993714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F680p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F14c880e956fe12725413ff47722f7518%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2020%2F06%2F10%2F490296%2Fi_src_036993714.jpg&h=b05d7bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4e19ea31887f99b17d59cff0893a84eeef96a7","tid":2488055,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"退休公務員在前年6月反修例示威一周年當天，群眾在旺角聚集期間，帶頭叫喊「黑警死全家」等口號。他今在西九龍裁判法院承認在公眾地方作出擾攘秩序的行為罪，被判囚40 天。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，事發當日晚上，逾 200名示威者聚集旺角港鐵站 E1出口外。未幾人潮漸漸散去，驟降至 50 人以下，被告便帶頭叫口號，亦有人扮狗吠及講粗口和應。警方發現後警告他停止，被告隨即轉身逃跑，但最終被捕。"},{"pid":"1f54e79ac9ec6ba0e677b9525196742e16b00744","tid":2488055,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:04:43.000Z","msg":"oh... 死黑警"},{"pid":"63608166cb1f62efff0d7e6edc745a30a24e4ea7","tid":2488055,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T06:06:47.000Z","msg":"辯方呈上多封求情信指，被告過去 26 年擔任公僕，在港九新界各區奔波，為市民服務，因此患上靜脈曲張及其他小毛病。他去年退休後，一時衝動、受社會氣氛影響而犯下本案，現已感到相當後悔，更因此寢食難安。他被定罪後，亦很可能面臨失去部分或全部的退休金。<br />\n<br />\n辯方續指，被告女兒觀察到父親失眠的狀況，亦深知他有悔意，不敢再踏足案發地點。與被告共事多年的前上司形容，他富責任心，具良好品格，非常滿意其工作表現。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，被告初犯，一生奉公守法，生活因此有轉變，相信他已汲取教訓。他的家人認為，被告受社會氣氛影響，不知如何宣洩積壓已久的情緒，最終犯下案件。裁判官又指，案發當日多人聚集叫囂，有人更從高處擲物，形成警民對峙的局面，考慮到被告擔當領導角色，帶頭叫口號的舉措令現場氣氛更見緊張，甚至引發暴力的風險。裁判官明言，即使他受本案困擾，很可能喪失退休金，亦決定判處即時監禁，並將量到起點定於 60 天，扣減認罪刑期後，總刑期為 40 天。<br />\n<br />\n陶亦被指與群眾一唱一和高叫「支持香港警察！吞槍自殺！」及「好警唔當差！當差正仆街！」等口號。其後警方直指著陶，警告他停止，但他沒有理會，繼而轉身逃跑，但最終被捕。警誡下他保持緘默。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E7%AB%99%E5%A4%96%E5%8F%AB-%E6%AD%BB%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E5%85%AC%E5%83%95%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-40-%E5%A4%A9-%E5%AE%98-%E5%B8%B6%E9%A0%AD%E5%8F%AB%E5%8F%A3%E8%99%9F%E5%BC%95%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258F%25AB-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2583%2595%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-40-%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E5%258F%25AB%25E5%258F%25A3%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1Tvbkzvov2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=21cc199f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258F%25AB-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%25BB%2591%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%2583%2595%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%2